<p>The Policy Aide is <strong>Unit 4's voice + defense partner</strong>. It coaches you to translate climate science into the policy-brief voice an actual Greater Chennai Corporation official would expect — direct, audience-aware, recommendation-anchored, no academic-essay creep. Then role-plays the tough panel questions before Block 12's live defense: cost, feasibility, equity, science credibility.</p>

